The paper presents faster algorithms for computing $\ell_p$-norm minimizing flows and $\ell_p$-norm regression problems. These problems are related to graph algorithms, numerical analysis, machine learning, and information theory, which are covered by the sub-categories of cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.LG, cs.CC, and cs.IT. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
